<li><strong>Edinburgh University worthies : biographies of selected pre-1901 alumni and staff of the University of Edinburgh</strong> (1999) (not available online - <a href="http://catalogue.lib.ed.ac.uk/vwebv/holdingsInfo?bibId=710789" target="_blank">local copies</a>)</li>
<li><strong>Medical education in the Age of Improvement : Edinburgh students and apprentices, 1760-1826</strong> - Lisa Rosner (1991) (not available online - <a href="http://catalogue.lib.ed.ac.uk/vwebv/holdingsInfo?bibId=429945" target="_blank">local copies</a>)</li>
